snippet.title: iPhone 6
snippet.description: We're tracking all of the rumors on specs, size, release date, and more for Apple's next iPhone.

snippet.title: HP Slate 6 VoiceTab
snippet.description: With a nice screen, good sound and dual SIM support, the HP Slate 6 VoiceTab aims to make some noise this May.

snippet.title: Asus ZenFone 6
snippet.description: CNET goes hands-on with the colorful Asus ZenFone smartphone family, which all sport an Intel Atom processor, Android 4.3, and expandable memory.

snippet.title: Exclusive: Nike fires majority of FuelBand team, will stop making wearable hardware
snippet.description: The sportswear company has decided that only software has a future in Nikeâ€™s technology vision. That means cutting the FuelBand, including a slimmer version planned for the fall.

snippet.title: Hamilton Beach Set 'n Forget 6-Quart Programmable Slow Cooker
snippet.description: The beauty of this affordable slow cooker is its simplicity. It sticks to the basics but also boasts extras that set it apart from the competition.

snippet.title: iOS 6
snippet.description: The transition to Apple Maps is rough, but new features and a ton of tiny tweaks make iOS 6 a must-have update.

snippet.title: TiVo reportedly lays off much of its hardware team
snippet.description: DVR maker has laid off "most" of its hardware engineers, according to Wired, but a spokesperson denies that the company is getting out of the hardware business.

snippet.title: Asus Fonepad Note FHD 6
snippet.description: The 6-inch phone-tablet hybrid will feature 3G connectivity and a 1080p screen.

snippet.title: Frigidaire Professional 6-Slice Convection Toaster Oven
snippet.description: The Frigidaire Professional 6-Slice Convection Toaster Oven's stainless steel finish and LCD screen may draw you in, but a major design flaw makes this toaster oven little more than a pretty face.

snippet.title: Sony Alpha NEX-6
snippet.description: The Sony Alpha NEX-6 delivers an as-yet-unbeatable package of image quality, performance, and design, even for its rather high price.
